&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chief Information Officer (CIO)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Chief Information Officer (CIO) provides the strategic vision and executive leadership for Plexus&#39; global technology organization, ensuring technology serves as a competitive advantage that accelerates business growth. This role is responsible for the end-to-end strategy, architecture, execution, and optimization of enterprise technology, business systems, infrastructure, cybersecurity, software engineering, and digital innovation across the organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a key member of the Executive Leadership Team, the CIO partners across every business function to align technology investments with corporate strategy, enabling Plexus&#39; Vision 2030 growth objectives and global expansion.&lt;/strong&gt; This leader will modernize the organization&#39;s technology ecosystem, leverage emerging technologies—including artificial intelligence and automation—and deliver world-class digital experiences for Brand Ambassadors and Customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equally important, the CIO builds and leads a high-performing global technology organization by attracting, developing, and retaining exceptional talent&lt;/strong&gt;. This leader fosters a culture of accountability, innovation, continuous learning, and collaboration, empowering teams to embrace emerging technologies while delivering measurable business outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is not a maintenance-focused technology role; it is a transformational leadership opportunity to shape the future of technology for a rapidly growing global organization.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This position requires full-time work from our Scottsdale, Arizona headquarters.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee Value Proposition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This is a unique opportunity to shape the future of Plexus technology as we pursue our Vision 2030 to become the world&#39;s leading gut health company and achieve &lt;strong&gt;$2 billion in revenue&lt;/strong&gt;. As Chief Information Officer, you won&#39;t simply maintain technology; you&#39;ll define how it accelerates business growth. You&#39;ll lead enterprise-wide digital transformation, evaluate and implement emerging technologies to create lasting competitive advantage, and build scalable platforms that power exceptional experiences for millions of Brand Ambassadors and Customers worldwide.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Partnering closely with an exceptional Executive Leadership Team, you&#39;ll influence enterprise strategy, support expansion across APAC, LATAM, and Europe, and champion innovation through artificial intelligence, automation, and modern technolog

