&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Director, Marketing – Mexico&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for developing and executing the localized marketing strategy that drives brand awareness, customer engagement, Brand Ambassador growth, and long-term business performance across the Mexico market. This leader creates a consistent, culturally relevant marketing vision that strengthens Plexus&#39; position as the leading gut health brand while equipping Brand Ambassadors with the tools, campaigns, and resources they need to successfully grow their businesses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Serving as the strategic marketing leader for Mexico, this role partners closely with Global Marketing, Brand, Product Development, Sales, and Field Development teams to translate global initiatives into impactful local campaigns that resonate with Mexican consumers and Brand Ambassadors.&lt;/strong&gt; The Director also leads the market&#39;s digital marketing strategy, ensuring Plexus builds a recognizable online presence through localized social media, digital content, and customer engagement initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Fully bilingual in English and Spanish, this leader combines strategic thinking, creativity, operational excellence, and people leadership to accelerate business growth while ensuring brand consistency and regulatory compliance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee Value Proposition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a unique opportunity to shape the future of one of Plexus&#39; most important international markets by building one of Mexico&#39;s most recognizable gut health brands. As &lt;strong&gt;Director, Marketing – Mexico&lt;/strong&gt;, you will define the local marketing strategy, create culturally relevant campaigns that inspire Brand Ambassadors and customers, and lead the market&#39;s digital growth. Working closely with global Marketing, Brand, Product Development, and Sales leaders, you&#39;ll transform global initiatives into meaningful local impact. If you&#39;re passionate about building brands, driving customer engagement, and delivering measurable business results, this role offers the opportunity to leave a lasting mark on Plexus&#39;s growth in Mexico.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Performance Objectives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The successful candidate will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Establish Plexus as one of the most recognized and trusted gut health brands in Mexico.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Increase brand awareness, customer engagement, and digital reach through localized marketing and social media strategies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
