&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Director, Sales – Mexico, is responsible for developing and executing the market sales strategy to accelerate revenue growth, strengthen Brand Ambassador engagement, and build&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a sustainable leadership pipeline across Mexico. This role leads a team of Field Development Specialists while partnering closely with Marketing, Sales Operations, Compliance, and Customer Experience to deliver a consistent, localized field experience that drives enrollments, retention, activation, and rank advancement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Success in this role requires a highly visible leader who thrives in the field, builds trusted relationships, and inspires action through coaching, education, recognition, and strategic execution. By combining regional events, leadership development, and virtual engagement, this leader will help relaunch and expand one of Plexus&#39; highest growth opportunities. This position requires up to 20% travel throughout Mexico and full bilingual fluency in English and Spanish.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee Value Proposition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to Make an Impact?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a unique opportunity to build something meaningful. As Director, Sales – Mexico, you&#39;ll have the autonomy to shape the sales strategy, develop future field leaders, and accelerate the growth of an established global brand in one of its greatest expansion opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Supported by science-backed products, a trusted reputation, and global resources, you&#39;ll play a pivotal role in relaunching the Mexico market while creating opportunities for thousands of Brand Ambassadors to grow successful businesses. If you&#39;re energized by building teams, coaching leaders, and creating measurable business results, you&#39;ll have the opportunity to leave a lasting impact while continuing to grow your own career.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Performance Objectives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The successful candidate will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop and execute&lt;/strong&gt; a scalable sales strategy that delivers sustained revenue growth across Mexico.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Increase Brand Ambassador enrollments, activation, retention, and

&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Join our Talent Community&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;When we find great people, we want to connect with them and keep the conversation going.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for exceptional individuals to help lead Plexus Worldwide today and into the future. We invite you to join our Talent Community and become a part of our growing network. Stay informed of Plexus Worldwide news, special events, and business topics that may interest you. Our Talent Acquisition team will keep you updated on opportunities that align with your career aspirations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Happiness lives where communities thrive. At Plexus, community is our culture.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;

